cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference SupraCloud IRA in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "SupraCloud IRA: a local-first personal AI assistant"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Kamineti"
    given-names: "Praveen"
    alias: "Praveen Kumar"
repository-code: "https://github.com/Praveenkumar101508/Supracloud_ira"
abstract: >-
  SupraCloud IRA is a private, local-first AI assistant that runs local models by
  default (Ollama-native tiers), routes each request to the right model for the job,
  uses ranked reference-only memory, and gates every external API call and destructive
  action behind explicit owner consent. Chat, voice, memory, research, and actions run
  on the owner's own hardware.
keywords:
  - local-first
  - ai-assistant
  - privacy
  - llm
  - fastapi
  - langgraph
version: "1.0.0"
